            <h1>Consumers</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/forbruker_150x113.jpg" alt="Use of bankcard" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">The chief goals of consumer policy are to promote consumers’ rights, interests and safety. </p>
            <img src="/Upload/PORTAL/Temabilder/forbruker_150x113.jpg" alt="Use of bankcard" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p>Consumer policy cuts across organisational boundaries and involves issues that are the responsibility of a number of different ministries. <em>The</em> <em>Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion</em> endeavours to strengthen consumer rights, interests and safety. </p>
<p>On this page you will find general information and documents relating to consumer policy. You can explore this topic in more detail by using the menu on the right.</p></div>
